OL,3,CPSNI chief believes workload
OL,4,Ccontributed to officer taking their
OL,5,Cown life
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's police chief has
OL,8,Fsaid he believes that workload
OL,9,Frecently contributed to an officer
OL,10,Ftaking their own life.
OL,12,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,13,F(PSNI) Chief Constable Jon Boutcher
OL,14,Foutlined his concern at having just
OL,15,F6,300 officers, well short of the
OL,16,Frecommended 7,500, amid growing
OL,17,Fdemands.
OL,19,FHe said the additional workload
OL,20,Fincludes taking 500 calls a month for
OL,21,Fthe Ambulance Service.
