OL,7,FMr Boutcher described policing as
OL,8,Fbeing in a "really tough place" and
OL,9,Fsaid the PSNI is being left behind
OL,10,Fother police forces in Great Britain
OL,11,Fand the Republic of Ireland in terms
OL,12,Fof budget increases, adding those
OL,13,Fforces did not have to contend with
OL,14,Fthe additional security threat faced
OL,15,Fby officers in the region.
OL,17,FOn the day the Stormont budget was
OL,18,Funveiled, Mr Boutcher also expressed
OL,19,Fconcern that further funding which is
OL,20,Fneeded would not be forthcoming.
