OL,7,FAppearing at the Assembly's justice
OL,8,Fcommittee, Mr Boutcher said he is
OL,9,Foften challenged at the Northern
OL,10,FIreland Policing Board about having
OL,11,Fthe highest sickness levels in the UK
OL,12,Fin terms of police forces.
OL,14,FHe said that is a "direct correlation"
OL,15,Fto levels of demand and workload,
OL,16,Fdescribing much of the sickness as
OL,17,F"simply tiredness, exhaustion and
OL,18,Fstress" due to the nature of the
OL,19,Fcaseload that officers are carrying.
